0 MAP~
{YSyntax:{x {Pmap{x

This command displays a small map of the local area. At
the centre of the map is the {Y*{x symbol. That's you!
Around the {Y*{x you will find a few symbols relating
the surrounding environment.

The numbers represent the number of people (mobs and players) in a given room.
